<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbffc59e9-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idbffc59ea-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2014—Subsec. (c)(2)(A). <ref href="/us/pl/113/79">Pub. L. 113–79</ref> substituted “section 8102(b)” for “section 8102(h)(1)”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
